# Docker build context hygiene.
#
# The build only needs Go sources, go.mod/go.sum, the baked fly config and
# the entrypoint. Everything below is either not a build input or must never
# leave this machine. Without this file `COPY . .` uploads the whole tree —
# including the local-only agent files — to the (remote) builder, even
# though it never lands in the final image. `make deploy` also builds
# locally so the context stays on this machine; this is defense-in-depth.

.git
.github
.gitignore

# Local-only agent files (gitignored) — must never leave this machine.
.claude
CLAUDE.md
PROGRESS.md
SHOTLIST.md

# Build outputs, recorded benchmarks — heavy, not build inputs.
bin
bench

# Demo/dev orchestration and scripts — not needed to build the binaries.
demo
scripts
docker-compose.dev.yml
docker-compose.demo.yml

# Docs and local env.
*.md
.env
